[normal]How should the Highways Agency be reformed[bold]&#xa0;[bold]to make it “the world’s leading highway operator”? What roles should Government and the private sector play to ensure better management of the strategic road network?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]G
[normal]iven that the majority of roads in the UK are controlled by Local Highway Authorities any reforms to the Highways Agency should have a role for the Local Highway Authority as part of an assurance framework.
